      {"id": "GeqrPrMDBg2kxvhG", "content": {"type": "Text", "format": "html", "text": ["<strong>Situation B. Using the Constant of Proportionality: Best Buy for Pasta</strong>", "<p>Mia is shopping for pasta. She sees two advertisements:</p>"]}},
